OL,3,CLiverpool hospital treating teens for
OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,FThat's the relief of a 27-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman who has finally been able to
OL,8,Fdiscard her adult nappies for the
OL,9,Ffirst time in months after undergoing
OL,10,Ftreatment to help repair her bladder
OL,11,Fafter using the drug, ketamine.
OL,13,FShe's just one of many young people
OL,14,Fwho are being treatment at a brand new
OL,15,Fbespoke ketamine clinic at Aintree
OL,16,FHospital, opened specifically to treat
OL,17,Fthose who have been damaged by the
OL,18,Fdrug.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
