OL,6,F"I've just finished an on-call run,
OL,7,Fand I had the biggest number I've ever
OL,8,Fseen of in-patient ketamine users,"
OL,9,Fexplains Katie Moore, a consultant
OL,10,Furologist at the site.
OL,12,F"We're seeing these young people whose
OL,13,Fpain can't be managed as a result of
OL,14,Fhaving taken the drug, and so they
OL,15,Fresort to taking more ketamine."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
