OL,3,CLiverpool hospital treating teens for
OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,FThe drug can lead to something called
OL,7,F'ketamine bladder', where the drug
OL,8,Fstarts to shred and scar the bladder
OL,9,Fafter use, which can lead to
OL,10,Fshrinking, and in turn, sometimes
OL,11,Fsevere pain.
OL,13,F"These appointments take a lot longer
OL,14,Fbecause patients are running to the
OL,15,Ftoilet every five minutes," nurse
OL,16,FAmbre Au-Delves tells me.
OL,18,FThis is a result of the small amount
OL,19,Fof liquid a young person's bladder can
OL,20,Fnow hold, although the specific impact
OL,21,Fvaries from patient to patient.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
