OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,FKetamine is an anaesthetic, often
OL,7,Fknown as a horse tranquilliser, that
OL,8,Fhas hallucinogenic effects.
OL,10,FIt's also a Class B drug, with the
OL,11,Fmaximum penalty for supplying and
OL,12,Fproducing it up to 14 years in prison,
OL,13,Fan unlimited fine, or both.
OL,15,FWe've been granted exclusive access to
OL,16,FAintree Hospital, as the government
OL,17,Fconsiders evidence from their expert
OL,18,Fadvisory panel about whether to bring
OL,19,Fketamine in line with other substances
OL,20,Flike Cocaine and MDMA and reclassify
OL,21,Fit as a Class A drug.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
