OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,FEarlier this year, we learnt the
OL,7,Fketamine crisis was "overwhelming"
OL,8,Fauthorities in the north west of
OL,9,FEngland, as children as young as
OL,10,Ftwelve were becoming addicted to the
OL,11,Fdrug.
OL,13,FAt the time, local leaders told us the
OL,14,Fdrug was so cheap and accessible,
OL,15,Fschool-aged children were opting to
OL,16,Fbuy it instead of crisps or a fizzy
OL,17,Fdrink.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
