OL,3,CLiverpool hospital treating teens for
OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,FAnd the problem in the north-west
OL,7,Fhasn't gone away, with several
OL,8,Fcouncils recently declaring they had
OL,9,Fbeen taking emergency action to tackle
OL,10,Fthe issue. It's meant ketamine support
OL,11,Fgroups have been set up in several
OL,12,Fboroughs across Liverpool and
OL,13,FLancashire.
OL,15,FOne in Skelmersdale takes place each
OL,16,Fweek and is chaired by 22-year-old
OL,17,FMegan Taylor, who started taking
OL,18,Fketamine not long after her 18th
OL,19,Fbirthday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
