OL,6,F"I was ready to die, I wanted it to
OL,7,Fkill me. I used to wake up being angry
OL,8,Fthat I was still alive."
OL,10,FMegan has now been clean for more than
OL,11,Fsix months, but ketamine's effect on
OL,12,Fher bladder is still being felt.
OL,14,F"I'm still going to the toilet every
OL,15,F20-30 minutes, sometimes every 2-5
OL,16,Fminutes," Meghan says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
