OL,6,FThe families at this meeting thought
OL,7,Fmoving the drug up to a Class A may
OL,8,Fhelp in curbing some of its use among
OL,9,Fthe young, but ultimately more
OL,10,Fteaching around the harms in schools
OL,11,Fis needed.
OL,13,F"It's a complete waste of time."
OL,15,FDuring my investigation, I've met some
OL,16,Ffamilies who don't believe upgrading
OL,17,Fketamine to a Class A will have a
OL,18,Fpositive impact.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
