OL,3,CLiverpool hospital treating teens for
OL,4,Cketamine as drug could be made Class A
OL,6,F"When ketamine was upgraded from a
OL,7,FClass C to a Class B, usage went up
OL,8,Fenormously.
OL,10,F"No one's really saying, 'I won't take
OL,11,Fthis because it's Class A or B'.
OL,12,FPeople are always going to take drugs."
OL,14,FVicky's daughter, Louise died back in
OL,15,F2011 after taking ketamine as an art
OL,16,Fstudent.
OL,18,FSince her daughter's death, Vicky has
OL,19,Fbeen campaigning relentlessly for
OL,20,Fgreater harm reduction and education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
