OL,6,F"What's much more effective is to
OL,7,Fcampaign for harm reduction, to make
OL,8,Fyoung people aware of the dangers of
OL,9,Fbecoming addicted or of getting
OL,10,Fketamine-bladder or of never being
OL,11,Fable to have sex ever again, it just
OL,12,Fruins your life," she says.
OL,14,F"And the criminalisation of ketamine
OL,15,Fwill prevent people from getting help."
OL,17,FOn January 3, 2024, drag star The
OL,18,FVivienne was found dead.
OL,20,FTheir family later revealed they had
OL,21,Fdied as a result of ketamine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
