OL,6,F"My brother passed away as a result of
OL,7,Fketamine, and as soon as I knew that
OL,8,Fwas the reason, I really wanted to
OL,9,Fmake a change," says Chanel Williams.
OL,11,FSince then, she has been campaigning
OL,12,Fto get the drug uplifted to a Class A
OL,13,Fby the Home Office, and her
OL,14,Fdetermination is evident.
OL,16,F"I'm the Vivienne's sister, and I
OL,17,Fwon't stop until I see the change that
OL,18,Fis needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
