OL,6,F"We need to be reviewing how we
OL,7,Feducate children in schools on drugs,
OL,8,Ftheir harms and ensuring there's lived
OL,9,Fexperience as part of that teaching."
OL,11,FWe reached out to the Home Office for
OL,12,Fan update on their approach to
OL,13,Fketamine and a a government
OL,14,Fspokesperson told ITV News: "Ketamine
OL,15,Fis an extremely dangerous substance
OL,16,Fand the recent rise in its use is
OL,17,Fdeeply concerning.
